```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Welcome</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; color: #333; }

    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px 60px;
      background: #fff;
    }
    nav a {
      margin-left: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #555;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    nav a.cta {
      background: #2563eb;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4ff 0%, #e8f0fe 100%);
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #111;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #555;
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .hero .btns .btn-primary {
      background: #2563eb;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 36px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .hero .btns .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: #2563eb;
      padding: 14px 36px;
      border: 2px solid #2563eb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-left: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div style="font-weight:800;font-size:1.3rem;">Brandname</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#">Features</a>
      <a href="#">Pricing</a>
      <a href="#">About</a>
      <a href="#" class="cta">Get Started</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Build something<br />people will love.</h1>
    <p>Everything you need to launch faster, scale smarter, and grow stronger — all in one place.</p>
    <div class="btns">
      <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Start Free Trial</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
```
